{"tid":1482342,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳茂波：經濟措施不足以回應政治訴求","createTime":"2019-08-18T05:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T06:27:28.000Z","uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"27eb3604e229c0033d730e84124af1034cace8ae","tid":1482342,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:12:42.000Z","msg":"面對香港經濟下行，政府推出191億元「撐企業、紓民困」措施，<span style=\"color: red;\">財政司司長陳茂波表示，措施不足以回應政治訴求。</span><br />\n<br />\n陳茂波出席無綫節目《講清講楚》時稱，現在面對政治困難，<span style=\"color: red;\">政治問題仍需一個政治解決方案</span>。他推出一系列的經濟措施，是針對現在見到的經濟環境和未來預計的經濟大困難而推出，這些措施不足以回應大家政治上的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，免卻一些牌費，以及商店因遇到示威各樣情況要停業、要關門相比，真的杯水車薪。他希望社會能早日回復平靜，大家暫時放下一些分歧，一起努力解決正面對的經濟困難。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/2223528/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2223528%2F&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPBZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=56563b90\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/2223528/</a>"},{"pid":"d045615f577289585b9999418e56b7034593b3d1","tid":1482342,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:13:46.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n可以賽後檢討，但<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>It is now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">風雨不改！2PM！WAI YUEN GIN！ </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hrJrLgG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhrJrLgG.jpg&h=d354981c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GMZbbWG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGMZbbWG.jpg&h=b5e6b6ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50bf4e3c0e2db4453b7ef47930b670